ements persist but decel-\nerate to approximately +0.45% per call as the system nears\nits performance ceiling. Beyond 6 calls, each additional call\nyields less than 0.15% performance gain. DTR operates at\nan average of4.78calls, effectively positioning it within\nthe optimal transition region where quality and computation\nare balanced. In contrast, the CodeLoop baseline exhibits\na failure mode characteriz","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
